# data/osint.db is intentionally tracked -- the scheduled GitHub Action
# commits it back on each run, so the commit history itself is evidence
# the automated pipeline is actually running. Keep local scratch DBs
# (from ad-hoc testing) out with a different filename if you don't want
# them tracked, e.g. data/scratch.db.
